## Semantic Kernel + RAG

### Kernel Setup
```csharp
var kernel = Kernel.CreateBuilder()
    .AddAzureOpenAIChatCompletion(deploymentName, endpoint, apiKey)
    .AddAzureOpenAITextEmbeddingGeneration(embeddingModel, endpoint, apiKey)
    .Build();
```

### RAG Pattern (TextSearchProvider)
```csharp
// 1. Vector Store olustur
var vectorStore = new RedisVectorStore(redisConnection);
var collection = vectorStore.GetCollection<string, DocumentChunk>("knowledge");

// 2. Dokuman embedding'lerini indexle
var embeddings = await kernel.GetRequiredService<ITextEmbeddingGenerationService>()
    .GenerateEmbeddingsAsync(chunks);
await collection.UpsertBatchAsync(chunks.Zip(embeddings, (c, e) => new DocumentChunk
{
    Id = c.Id, Text = c.Text, Embedding = e
}));

// 3. Sorgu zamani: TextSearchProvider ile RAG
var textSearch = new VectorStoreTextSearch<DocumentChunk>(collection, embeddings);
var searchPlugin = textSearch.CreateWithGetTextSearchResults("SearchKnowledge");
kernel.Plugins.Add(searchPlugin);

// 4. Agent ile kullan
var agent = new ChatCompletionAgent
{
    Name = "Assistant",
    Instructions = "Cevaplarini bilgi tabanindan al. Kaynak belirt.",
    Kernel = kernel
};
```

