## Data Drift Detection
```
Izleme Metrikleri:
├── Feature Distribution: KS test, PSI (Population Stability Index)
├── Prediction Distribution: ortalama ve varyans kayması
├── Model Performance: basari metrigi dususu (RMSE, F1)

Tetikleyiciler:
├── PSI > 0.2 -> UYARI, modeli incele
├── PSI > 0.5 -> KRITIK, yeniden egit
├── Performance drop > %10 -> Yeniden egitim tetikle
```

## Model Versioning
```
models/
├── demand-forecast/
│   ├── v1.0/
│   │   ├── model.zip
│   │   ├── metadata.json (metriks, training date, data hash)
│   │   └── evaluation.json (test set results)
│   └── v1.1/
│       └── ...
├── anomaly-detection/
│   └── v1.0/
```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Train on all data | Train/test/validation split |
| No cross-validation | k-fold CV (k=5) |
| Feature in prod but not train | Feature store + pipeline |
| No model monitoring | Drift detection + alerts |
| LLM for simple rules | Rule-based when deterministic |
| No prompt versioning | Version control prompts |
| Single model forever | Scheduled retraining |

